<subSubSection id="9A85652DFFD6FFE6B0AFFE94E435FCBF" pageId="2" pageNumber="5" type="description">
<paragraph id="D22036A6FFD6FFE6B0AFFE94E245FEDC" blockId="2.[166,1225,287,826]" pageId="2" pageNumber="5">E t y m o l o g y. The species is named in honour of the Late Dr. F. Schmid, who contributed much to the taxonomy of caddisflies of the Indian subcontinent.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D22036A6FFD6FFE6B0AFFED4E413FE1F" blockId="2.[166,1225,287,826]" pageId="2" pageNumber="5">
F e m a l e. Head with antennae 
<quantity id="15679B43FFD6FFE6B236FED4E4DCFEFF" box="[578,702,351,378]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.85" metricValueMax="1.9" metricValueMin="1.8" pageId="2" pageNumber="5" unit="mm" value="18.5" valueMax="19.0" valueMin="18.0">18–19 mm</quantity>
long. Forewings 
<quantity id="15679B43FFD6FFE6B3F5FED4E59CFEFF" box="[897,1022,351,378]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.1" metricValueMax="2.2" metricValueMin="2.0" pageId="2" pageNumber="5" unit="mm" value="21.0" valueMax="22.0" valueMin="20.0">20–22 mm</quantity>
Wings yellowish; body darker brown than head and legs.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D22036A6FFD6FFE6B0AFFE14E42FFD9F" blockId="2.[166,1225,287,826]" pageId="2" pageNumber="5">F e m a l e a b d o m e n. Segment VIII completely divided into tergite and sternite. Segment IX apodemes extending anteriorly to segment VII. Apex of segment X in lateral view rounded in outline and with indentation. Vaginal apparatus with posterior apex rounded and anterior base truncate.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D22036A6FFD6FFE6B0AFFD94E435FCBF" blockId="2.[166,1225,287,826]" pageId="2" pageNumber="5">
D i a g n o s i s. The female of this species does not closely resemble any species of 
<taxonomicName id="159F4D25FFD6FFE6B0D2FDB4E72BFDDC" authorityName="Banks" authorityYear="1940" box="[166,329,575,601]" class="Insecta" family="Rhyacophilidae" genus="Himalopsyche" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="5" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="E0EBEAB4FFD6FFE6B0D2FDB4E72BFDDC" box="[166,329,575,601]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="5">Himalopsyche</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but shows some similarity to 
<taxonomicName id="159F4D25FFD6FFE6B2A7FDCBE224FDDF" authority="Schmid, 1963" authorityName="Schmid" authorityYear="1963" box="[723,1094,575,602]" class="Insecta" family="Rhyacophilidae" genus="Himalopsyche" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="5" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dolmasampa">
<emphasis id="E0EBEAB4FFD6FFE6B2A7FDCBE5F3FDDC" box="[723,913,575,601]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="5">H. dolmasampa</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="B60E4B57FFD6FFE6B3EAFDB4E224FDDF" author="Schmid, F." box="[926,1094,575,602]" pageId="2" pageNumber="5" pagination="206 - 223" refId="ref8049" refString="Schmid, F. Quelques Himalopsyche indiennes (Trichopteres, Rhyacophilidae) // Bonner Zoologische Beitrage. - 1963. - 14. - P. 206 - 223." type="book chapter" year="1963">Schmid, 1963</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. However, these can be separated from each other on the basis of the morphology of the genitalia in lateral view and the vaginal apparatus in ventral view. The apex of segments X in new species is rounded whereas in 
<taxonomicName id="159F4D25FFD6FFE6B26CFD2BE4B6FD3C" authorityName="Schmid" authorityYear="1963" box="[536,724,671,697]" class="Insecta" family="Rhyacophilidae" genus="Himalopsyche" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="5" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dolmasampa">
<emphasis id="E0EBEAB4FFD6FFE6B26CFD2BE4B6FD3C" box="[536,724,671,697]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="5">H. dolmasampa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
the apex is not so rounded. The anterior base of the vaginal apparatus is without a pointed projection in 
<taxonomicName id="159F4D25FFD6FFE6B3EEFD4BE27AFD5C" authority="Lakhwinder &amp; Malkiat, 2015" authorityName="Lakhwinder &amp; Malkiat" authorityYear="2015" box="[922,1048,703,729]" class="Insecta" family="Rhyacophilidae" genus="Himalopsyche" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="5" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="schmidi" status="sp. n.">
<emphasis id="E0EBEAB4FFD6FFE6B3EEFD4BE27AFD5C" box="[922,1048,703,729]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="5">H. schmidi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="E0EBEAB4FFD6FFE6B454FD34E200FD5C" bold="true" box="[1056,1122,703,729]" pageId="2" pageNumber="5">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="FBD857CFFFD6FFE6B454FD34E200FD5C" box="[1056,1122,703,729]" pageId="2" pageNumber="5" rank="species">sp. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
whereas 
<taxonomicName id="159F4D25FFD6FFE6B0D2FD6BE703FD7C" authorityName="Schmid" authorityYear="1963" box="[166,353,735,761]" class="Insecta" family="Rhyacophilidae" genus="Himalopsyche" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="5" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dolmasampa">
<emphasis id="E0EBEAB4FFD6FFE6B0D2FD6BE703FD7C" box="[166,353,735,761]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="5">H. dolmasampa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has a pointed projection. Anterior margin of sternum VIII with slightly raised projection in 
<taxonomicName id="159F4D25FFD6FFE6B1ECFC8BE431FC9C" authorityName="Schmid" authorityYear="1963" box="[408,595,767,793]" class="Insecta" family="Rhyacophilidae" genus="Himalopsyche" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="5" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dolmasampa">
<emphasis id="E0EBEAB4FFD6FFE6B1ECFC8BE431FC9C" box="[408,595,767,793]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="5">H. dolmasampa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
where as in 
<taxonomicName id="159F4D25FFD6FFE6B29AFC8BE50FFC9C" authority="Lakhwinder &amp; Malkiat, 2015" authorityName="Lakhwinder &amp; Malkiat" authorityYear="2015" box="[750,877,767,793]" class="Insecta" family="Rhyacophilidae" genus="Himalopsyche" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="5" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="schmidi" status="sp. n.">
<emphasis id="E0EBEAB4FFD6FFE6B29AFC8BE50FFC9C" box="[750,877,767,793]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="5">H. schmidi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="E0EBEAB4FFD6FFE6B302FD74E5DBFC9C" bold="true" box="[886,953,767,793]" pageId="2" pageNumber="5">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="FBD857CFFFD6FFE6B302FD74E5DBFC9C" box="[886,953,767,793]" pageId="2" pageNumber="5" rank="species">sp. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
the anterior margin is truncate and without any projection.
</paragraph>
